cs.CR, cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.LG 

This paper deals with privacy and security challenges in crowdsourcing markets, which are related to cryptography and game theory (cs.CR and cs.GT). The paper also proposes a mechanism for determining prices of tasks, which involves artificial intelligence and machine learning techniques (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the allocation of tasks to workers, which is related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed mechanism, which involves statistical analysis and machine learning (cs.LG).
